1
00:00:09,320 --> 00:00:11,120
Have you discovered my secret?

2
00:00:11,360 --> 00:00:13,960
You tried so hard to marry into our Song family.

3
00:00:13,960 --> 00:00:15,160
What is your purpose?

4
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:17,860
Why are you targeting my brother?

5
00:00:19,880 --> 00:00:21,540
So, are you going to expose me?

6
00:00:28,360 --> 00:00:30,080
Since you know my secret,

7
00:00:31,280 --> 00:00:32,640
to be fair,

8
00:00:33,760 --> 00:00:36,440
let me tell you a secret about you.

9
00:00:37,240 --> 00:00:39,200
Stop playing tricks.

10
00:00:39,320 --> 00:00:40,560
If you don't explain everything about today

11
00:00:40,560 --> 00:00:41,720
clearly...

12
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:44,130
I'll teach you a lesson for my brother.

13
00:00:49,560 --> 00:00:51,420
How do you have my mother's photo?

14
00:00:51,520 --> 00:00:52,520
You know where she is.

15
00:00:52,520 --> 00:00:54,180
Not only do I know where she is,

16
00:00:54,520 --> 00:00:55,480
I also know

17
00:00:56,120 --> 00:00:57,720
what Song Huainan did to her.

18
00:00:57,920 --> 00:00:59,200
What exactly do you want?

19
00:00:59,200 --> 00:01:00,160
I want you

20
00:01:02,480 --> 00:01:03,680
to cooperate with me.

21
00:01:16,440 --> 00:01:17,200
Master.

22
00:01:17,800 --> 00:01:19,200
Master!

23
00:01:19,920 --> 00:01:21,200
My jade pendant is missing.

24
00:01:21,200 --> 00:01:22,600
I can't find it anywhere.

25
00:01:22,920 --> 00:01:23,680
Madam,

26
00:01:24,480 --> 00:01:25,940
we found the jade pendant.

27
00:01:26,280 --> 00:01:28,080
It was in Young Mistress's room.

28
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:32,000
Madam.

29
00:01:33,920 --> 00:01:36,680
Yao Shengsheng, what is the meaning of this?

30
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:37,560
We are family.

31
00:01:37,560 --> 00:01:39,360
If you wanted it, just tell me.

32
00:01:39,360 --> 00:01:41,490
It's not like I wouldn't give it to you.

33
00:01:41,960 --> 00:01:44,479
You can't just steal it because you like it.

34
00:01:44,479 --> 00:01:46,400
From what you're saying,

35
00:01:46,400 --> 00:01:48,840
taking things from someone else's room counts as stealing.

36
00:01:48,840 --> 00:01:50,240
You don't consider this stealing?

37
00:01:50,240 --> 00:01:52,560
Since this jade pendant is from Huainan's room,

38
00:01:52,560 --> 00:01:55,240
and Stepmother took it, that counts as stealing too.

39
00:01:55,240 --> 00:01:57,000
You're twisting my words.

40
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:58,000
Huainan gave this to me as a gift.

41
00:01:58,000 --> 00:01:58,560
Enough.

42
00:02:00,560 --> 00:02:01,720
What's there to argue about?

43
00:02:01,720 --> 00:02:03,520
With such a big family business,

44
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:06,000
you're arguing over a jade pendant.

45
00:02:06,320 --> 00:02:09,039
If word gets out, we'll be a laughing stock.

46
00:02:09,039 --> 00:02:11,240
Huainan, you're so biased.

47
00:02:11,240 --> 00:02:13,960
You gave such a nice jade pendant to Stepmother.

48
00:02:14,320 --> 00:02:16,360
As your wife, I'm so jealous.

49
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:18,280
You should have told me you liked it.

50
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:19,640
I'll find you a few better ones.

51
00:02:19,640 --> 00:02:21,079
But I like this one.

52
00:02:21,400 --> 00:02:22,480
This is mine.

53
00:02:23,320 --> 00:02:23,960
Forget it.

54
00:02:24,200 --> 00:02:27,040
I know you grew up with Stepmother.

55
00:02:27,040 --> 00:02:28,720
You must be very close.

56
00:02:29,160 --> 00:02:32,360
Maybe this jade pendant is a keepsake between you two.

57
00:02:33,079 --> 00:02:34,120
Even though I like it,

58
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:36,050
I shouldn't take what you cherish.

59
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:38,520
It's just that asking me to return it now...

60
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:40,560
I just couldn't bear to part with it.

61
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:42,079
What are you talking about?

62
00:02:42,079 --> 00:02:43,240
Stepmother is our elder.

63
00:02:43,240 --> 00:02:45,120
She said she liked it, so I just gave it to her.

64
00:02:45,120 --> 00:02:47,480
Since you like it so much, just take it.

65
00:02:48,280 --> 00:02:49,079
Thank you, Huainan.

66
00:02:49,079 --> 00:02:50,480
I knew you were good to me.

67
00:02:51,760 --> 00:02:52,520
Alright.

68
00:02:53,480 --> 00:02:54,000
Yuemei,

69
00:02:54,600 --> 00:02:55,329
come with me.

70
00:02:57,880 --> 00:02:58,440
Go back.

71
00:02:58,800 --> 00:02:59,800
Master.

72
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:30,580
Smells so good.

73
00:04:31,960 --> 00:04:32,720
Shengsheng.

74
00:04:34,640 --> 00:04:37,040
How much longer are you going to torture me?

75
00:04:41,200 --> 00:04:41,880
Huainan.

76
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:53,400
What you promised me earlier,

77
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:56,020
you can't go back on your word.

78
00:04:57,440 --> 00:04:59,159
I've drawn your bath.

79
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:01,440
Go take a bath first.

80
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:06,600
Okay.

81
00:05:08,440 --> 00:05:09,500
I'll go take a bath.

82
00:05:38,920 --> 00:05:42,640
Song Huainan, this is excellent aphrodisiac incense.

83
00:05:50,240 --> 00:05:51,560
Stepmother.

84
00:05:51,720 --> 00:05:53,360
Why are you in such a panic?

85
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:54,760
Huainan has a sudden splitting headache.

86
00:05:54,760 --> 00:05:55,760
Do you have any painkillers?

87
00:05:55,760 --> 00:05:57,600
I have some. I'll get them now.

88
00:05:57,760 --> 00:05:58,400
I'll call the doctor.

89
00:05:58,400 --> 00:05:59,730
Okay, I'll go right now.

90
00:06:29,760 --> 00:06:30,560
Shengsheng.

91
00:06:32,280 --> 00:06:33,240
Shengsheng.

92
00:06:41,920 --> 00:06:42,600
Huainan.

93
00:06:43,920 --> 00:06:46,600
Huainan, is your headache bad?

94
00:06:49,240 --> 00:06:50,840
I brought you some medicine.

95
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:56,720
Shengsheng,

96
00:06:58,480 --> 00:06:59,409
where did she go?

97
00:07:02,840 --> 00:07:03,520
Huainan.

98
00:07:44,800 --> 00:07:46,680
What are you doing?

99
00:07:48,320 --> 00:07:48,880
I...

100
00:07:50,760 --> 00:07:51,320
Master,

101
00:07:52,760 --> 00:07:53,800
let me explain.

102
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:54,440
Shut up,

103
00:07:54,720 --> 00:07:55,560
you slut.

104
00:07:55,840 --> 00:07:57,800
Master, there is really

105
00:07:57,800 --> 00:07:59,280
nothing going on between us.

106
00:07:59,280 --> 00:08:00,960
I didn't do anything, Master.

107
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:03,880
Huainan had a headache.

108
00:08:03,880 --> 00:08:05,740
I just came to bring him medicine.

109
00:08:06,920 --> 00:08:08,080
You slut.

110
00:08:08,720 --> 00:08:09,280
Guards!

111
00:08:10,520 --> 00:08:10,920
Master.

112
00:08:10,920 --> 00:08:12,520
Send the Madam to Xishan Villa.

113
00:08:12,520 --> 00:08:13,520
Without my order,

114
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:15,240
she is not to step foot in Song Manor.

115
00:08:15,240 --> 00:08:15,720
Master.

116
00:08:15,720 --> 00:08:16,450
Yes, Master.

117
00:08:16,760 --> 00:08:17,440
Master,

118
00:08:17,640 --> 00:08:18,800
I was wrong.

119
00:08:18,880 --> 00:08:20,560
Master, I know I was wrong.

120
00:08:21,080 --> 00:08:22,680
Please forgive me this time.

121
00:08:23,120 --> 00:08:23,720
Master.

122
00:08:35,799 --> 00:08:36,730
Yao Shengsheng,

123
00:08:37,080 --> 00:08:39,240
you've turned the Song Manor upside down.

124
00:08:39,240 --> 00:08:40,240
Are you happy now?

125
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:44,130
I'm just taking a tooth for a tooth,

126
00:08:44,520 --> 00:08:46,000
and an eye for an eye.

127
00:08:49,560 --> 00:08:51,360
What are you planning to do next?

128
00:08:58,160 --> 00:08:59,680
Letting you serve Mr. Johnson

129
00:08:59,680 --> 00:09:00,810
is doing you a favor.

130
00:09:00,960 --> 00:09:02,090
How dare you refuse?

131
00:09:02,600 --> 00:09:03,240
Sorry.

132
00:09:03,680 --> 00:09:05,240
I don't serve foreigners.

133
00:09:07,960 --> 00:09:09,960
I hate it when people hit women in front of me.

134
00:09:09,960 --> 00:09:11,440
You dare cause trouble here?

135
00:09:11,440 --> 00:09:12,480
You must have a death wish.

136
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:13,400
Go ask around.

137
00:09:13,640 --> 00:09:14,840
See if the Song family

138
00:09:15,080 --> 00:09:16,480
is qualified to cause trouble here.

139
00:09:16,480 --> 00:09:17,010
Get lost.

140
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:21,130
You're not Yao Shengsheng.

141
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:23,100
Did you find it?

142
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:26,200
The one who sent the message to Song Qingzhou is a dancer

143
00:09:26,200 --> 00:09:27,480
named Rose.

144
00:09:28,280 --> 00:09:29,610
Any other information?

145
00:09:29,960 --> 00:09:31,560
Johnson likes her very much.

146
00:09:32,080 --> 00:09:34,680
He seems to be making a deal with the Song family,

147
00:09:34,680 --> 00:09:36,880
and they are about to sign the contract.

148
00:09:37,160 --> 00:09:37,840
Contract?

149
00:09:38,400 --> 00:09:41,400
It seems Song Huainan sold a large plot of land in the suburbs

150
00:09:41,400 --> 00:09:42,760
privately to Johnson

151
00:09:42,760 --> 00:09:45,000
to grow some sort of raw material.

152
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:46,560
I'm not sure about the details.

153
00:09:46,560 --> 00:09:47,890
And the residents there

154
00:09:47,920 --> 00:09:49,380
have all been driven away.

155
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:57,000
How could you tell at a glance I wasn't Yao Shengsheng?

156
00:09:57,160 --> 00:09:58,880
Yao Shengsheng wants me dead.

157
00:09:59,240 --> 00:10:00,760
How could she possibly save me?

158
00:10:00,760 --> 00:10:01,720
And what about you?

159
00:10:01,720 --> 00:10:02,850
Do you want her dead?

160
00:10:03,120 --> 00:10:04,960
Yao Shengsheng wants me dead.

161
00:10:05,280 --> 00:10:07,120
Naturally, I want her dead too.

162
00:10:07,400 --> 00:10:08,840
Since you have a face

163
00:10:08,840 --> 00:10:10,800
identical to hers,

164
00:10:11,040 --> 00:10:13,920
I'd be happy to send you to hell.

165
00:10:14,080 --> 00:10:15,480
Marshal Song, over here.

166
00:10:16,800 --> 00:10:17,840
Where are they?

167
00:10:18,080 --> 00:10:20,040
I want to see who has the nerve

168
00:10:20,040 --> 00:10:22,440
to impersonate a member of the Song family.

169
00:10:23,520 --> 00:10:25,400
If Marshal Song knew

170
00:10:25,400 --> 00:10:27,160
he married a fake wife,

171
00:10:27,680 --> 00:10:28,880
would he...
